Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.62,0:01:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭与创造
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.38,0:01:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类何必总是重蹈覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很费解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类无法直面回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以美化它  夸大它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试图用怀念来包装疼痛以克服过去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要取回妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.13,0:02:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是出于怀念？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.45,0:02:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了克服眼前的难题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.16,0:02:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指星痕？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实归根到底是你们的错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.36,0:02:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你也惧怕回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健忘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.76,0:02:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾先生  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快瞧这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中头彩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真恶心啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点不行么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷诺  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈  快离开...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊利娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快走...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LifeStream
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是巡行在星球的生命之河
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星球和她滋养的  万物生灵的源头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神罗公司成功把LifeStream
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:05:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化作了能源
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托这个福  我们的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得丰富多彩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这却是在剥削星球的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反对者也为数不少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神罗对反对自己的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动用蛮力去压制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神罗麾下有一批特种兵  冠名为「战士」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很久以前从天而降
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以毁灭星球为己任的灾厄——
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰诺娃细胞的移植产物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫萨菲罗斯的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很是出类拔萃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  他得知了自己诞生于恐怖实验
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是对神罗怀恨在心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:06:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久而久之  他与一切事物不共戴天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神罗和反对它的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.35,0:06:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨菲罗斯不惜摧毁星球  只因仇深似海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多人竭力阻止萨菲罗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带来了无数战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争与悲剧形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也化作了LifeStream
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于在那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运之日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星球用自身的力量平息了一切干戈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星球把LifeStream用作武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喷出地面的LifeStream
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将纷争  野望  悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统统吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我们用悲伤圆上了句号」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已是两年前的安慰话了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.19,0:08:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过星球她...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远比我们想象的要愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星痕症候群
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  马琳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变什么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:08:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请留下丹泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据调查委今晨颁布的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大气中的LifeStream浓度仅为2年前的百分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经降至对人体毫无影响的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而神罗公司主楼...以及所属的周边地区
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:27.60,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里人去楼空哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然屹立于危险浓度中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了防患星痕症候群  请远离存在隐患的设施
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委员会如上警告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来报道神罗公司被追究的赔偿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德  你在哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  是Strife快递
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们服务广泛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.37,0:10:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然记得你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷诺从圆球别墅来电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要委托你工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德  你还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信息完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说卡达裘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是哥哥的镇？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们受欢迎么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对够呛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别掉泪啊  亚祖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈和他在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可难说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭啊  罗兹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧啊  说曹操曹操到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥给藏起来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你玩弄了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈果然在你们手里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.63,0:13:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懒得和你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换社长接
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.03,0:15:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是逃避了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  我是巴雷特 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子成功了  找到新油田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,油~田~  超级大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在有眉目了  不久就去见马琳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我转达一下  挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷诺又来电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,催你尽快去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有点怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己当心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有两下子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁德  大帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自封的原士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身手依旧不凡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.01,0:16:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是路法斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真背运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天我...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:55.86,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我何干
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大楼坍塌前  勉强...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.36,0:16:58.37,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁袭击的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:16:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼我走人么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮个忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:06.48,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们神罗公司欠世界一笔大债
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害得世界惨淡而寥落
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们把责任推给我们也合乎情理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是这笔债非还不可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:22.66,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开个门
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为第一步棋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们调查起萨菲罗斯遗留的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去两年了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界迈出了复兴的一步  什么构成了最大威胁？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  是万恶的星痕症候群
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们认为原因出在萨菲罗斯身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世人认为魔晄炉  魔晄能源
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及LifeStream是星痕的原因正在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看未必
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LifeStream与星球一起诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔晄能源更有40多年的利用史
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星痕在历史上从未有过登场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们这一代和有不同寻常？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不出别的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是萨菲罗斯的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨菲罗斯死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的精神去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溶解在了LifeStream中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若它未扩散而巡行在星球  那会怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  这终究是我的遐想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却不无可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知晓真相才会推动星痕的治愈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我们...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查了萨菲罗斯留下的蛛丝马迹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:18:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可曾记得？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方大空洞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜有何收获
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那儿一无所获
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过却节外生枝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们出现了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快...快走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡达裘一伙儿人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡达裘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他连你也不会放过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你与他们有过交手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是局外人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟早会物归原主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:47.59,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你与我们一样  与萨菲罗斯有很深的过往
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果卡达裘的目的是给来临的那一刻做铺垫...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们无疑是最大的障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铺垫？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨菲罗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卷土重来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么切入正题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.36,0:20:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了与卡达裘他们抗衡  我们需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何不并肩作战？原士兵·克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.38,0:20:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自封的罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.47,0:20:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡达裘他们挂在嘴上的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路法斯  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你隐瞒什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你我站在同一战线  我怎么会隐瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于星痕的情报想必你也需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.88,0:20:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了生活在同一屋檐下的孤儿们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.89,0:21:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让孩子们再次绽放笑颜如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的最终目的是重建世界  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.63,0:21:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托啦  克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让神罗公司东山再起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这个雅兴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.67,0:21:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷诺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.35,0:21:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德住在这儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.12,0:21:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.36,0:22:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.82,0:22:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和丹泽尔一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德也生病了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说一声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.12,0:22:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为病了  才出走的？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.97,0:22:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要独自去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.14,0:22:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.24,0:22:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他根本没有斗志
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.49,0:22:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂法？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.75,0:22:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去吧  马琳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.42,0:22:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我要见克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.85,0:23:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多想见见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.87,0:23:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见面之后怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.84,0:23:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拽他回家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.78,0:23:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过...说教在先
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.55,0:23:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.74,0:23:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要找主任和伊利娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他社员提供的情报呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.27,0:23:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时没有收获...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.98,0:23:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来的社员  来齐了这么多真是超出预料
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我泪流满面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.39,0:23:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看能重新来过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.54,0:23:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赎罪的重任  落在活下来的人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.80,0:23:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去两年了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.43,0:23:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.76,0:23:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才两年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.02,0:24:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那简直是噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.34,0:24:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界险些灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.10,0:24:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们神罗惹的祸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.02,0:24:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说真的  我们要赎多少罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.37,0:24:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少了主任果然很头疼啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.93,0:24:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊利娜也是  千万给我活的好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.22,0:24:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.81,0:24:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾先生和社长一样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.33,0:24:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九死一生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.82,0:24:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运气好的很
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.71,0:24:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.90,0:24:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.88,0:24:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教堂？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.88,0:25:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那个地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.97,0:25:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.44,0:26:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七号街的电话均无法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.32,0:26:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七号街的电话均无法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.50,0:26:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七号街的电话均无法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.60,0:26:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七号街的电话均无法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.83,0:27:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七号街的电话均无法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.96,0:27:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.93,0:27:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接到你的电话真是太阳打西边出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.39,0:27:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.92,0:27:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.06,0:27:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.48,0:27:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？这是克劳德的电话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.42,0:27:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.38,0:27:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.33,0:27:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.02,0:28:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道怎么办好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.06,0:28:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哭吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.22,0:28:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  你没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.22,0:28:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德  克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.04,0:28:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.83,0:28:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.89,0:28:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.73,0:29:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最烦说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.91,0:29:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.44,0:29:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我如实交代
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.54,0:29:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西在逃离你们的途中从飞机不慎掉落
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.96,0:29:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太失态了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.96,0:29:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当真么？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.60,0:29:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.72,0:29:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妨向这个发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.27,0:29:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的何在
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.83,0:29:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈的力量是必需的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.08,0:29:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了再聚合绝不能少
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.08,0:29:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(593,645)\fs45}Reunion
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.04,0:29:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再聚合
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.84,0:30:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得母亲细胞的同伴齐聚一堂
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.63,0:30:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后报复星球
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.64,0:30:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备工作稳步进行着
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.88,0:30:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧  都怪某些人把妈妈藏了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.69,0:30:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.50,0:30:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星痕
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.48,0:30:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长也颇有体会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.68,0:30:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这多亏在LifeStream中
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.61,0:30:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有妈妈的遗传意念在挣扎着
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.33,0:30:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再看看我们
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.19,0:30:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然不清楚妈妈在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.03,0:30:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢死人了  但却无可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.93,0:30:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让我们是区区意念体
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.72,0:30:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有找到妈妈后分得细胞
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.94,0:30:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能够复原
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.57,0:30:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光有意念和星痕远谈不上准备充分
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.82,0:30:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了完美的再聚合
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.08,0:30:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么乱糟糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.22,0:31:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长  您有所预感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.74,0:31:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.48,0:31:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  星痕
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.76,0:31:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别出门吓唬人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.11,0:32:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.73,0:32:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑在人在
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.61,0:32:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然下过决心...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.17,0:32:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成为战士啊  加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.17,0:32:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  感觉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.24,0:32:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  到达米德加尔后
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.60,0:32:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.73,0:32:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.02,0:33:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  找个岩石在后面停车
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.47,0:33:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德  我们下车
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.60,0:33:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的荣耀和梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.78,0:33:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.21,0:33:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.55,0:33:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见证了我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.65,0:33:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发誓过永不忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.29,0:33:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.23,0:33:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.82,0:33:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别假装悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.49,0:33:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无需演绎义愤填膺
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.14,0:33:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为克劳德...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.75,0:33:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.79,0:33:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.03,0:34:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来玩玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.21,0:34:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  不愿意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.56,0:34:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.45,0:34:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难闻
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.76,0:34:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.32,0:34:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这儿没有别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.42,0:34:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  来玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.86,0:35:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人沸腾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.82,0:36:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂法
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.62,0:36:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找错地方了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.20,0:37:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没哭
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.70,0:37:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我带她去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.74,0:37:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.61,0:38:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.74,0:38:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.06,0:38:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.42,0:38:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.91,0:38:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.15,0:38:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.68,0:38:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.64,0:38:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.10,0:38:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也得了星痕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.23,0:39:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人能治好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.90,0:39:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂法
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.48,0:39:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂法
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.71,0:40:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.25,0:40:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁干的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.83,0:40:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不认识他
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.30,0:40:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马琳
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.37,0:40:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.61,0:41:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉死我了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.44,0:41:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老兄  你跟孩子们生活的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.32,0:41:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.06,0:41:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袖手旁观？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.86,0:41:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.74,0:42:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽快些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.77,0:42:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂法要我带你过去
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.02,0:42:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧咯
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.48,0:43:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会治好我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.77,0:43:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.82,0:43:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  管他是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.24,0:43:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是哥哥藏的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.94,0:43:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从LifeStream中诞生的新力量
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.22,0:43:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让魔石球赐给我们新能力
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.79,0:43:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是母亲留给我们的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.44,0:43:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.94,0:44:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也被哥哥藏起来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.89,0:44:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是那个社长
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.02,0:44:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神罗公司一向喜欢把妈妈藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.69,0:44:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不妨把神罗的相关建筑搜个遍
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.24,0:44:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  更多伙伴会蜂拥而至
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.87,0:44:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.30,0:44:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过先要...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.90,0:44:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向哥哥发发牢骚
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.95,0:44:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装作自己是局外人
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.97,0:44:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.10,0:44:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.28,0:45:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷诺他们在四处打听
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.65,0:45:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星痕症候群  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.87,0:45:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了也无所谓吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.32,0:45:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.37,0:45:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有治愈的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.55,0:45:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  丹泽尔却从来不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.00,0:45:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起面对它不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.43,0:45:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相帮助  一起奋斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.73,0:45:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真正的家人  果然不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.13,0:45:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能...  谁也救不了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.30,0:45:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人也好  同伴也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.33,0:45:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都救不了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.85,0:46:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖拖拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.61,0:46:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖拖拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.53,0:46:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拖到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.69,0:46:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还找不到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.47,0:46:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有目击者称  是被那帮家伙带走的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.94,0:46:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.09,0:46:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘却之都
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.16,0:46:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们老家
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.12,0:46:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲眷顾我一份特殊力量
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.04,0:46:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能与折磨人的罪魁——星球作战的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.77,0:46:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你们也有这个能力
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.42,0:47:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.90,0:47:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.34,0:47:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承了溶解在LifeStream中  母亲遗传意念的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.35,0:47:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被选中的一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.91,0:47:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.80,0:47:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星球在百般阻挠
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.60,0:47:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它试图停止我们成长
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.81,0:47:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说  你们遭受皮肉之苦  痛不欲生
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.64,0:47:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你们治好
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.52,0:47:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后回到母亲身边
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.35,0:47:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家人齐心协力  报复星球
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.74,0:47:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着我做
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.56,0:48:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.18,0:48:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.42,0:48:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲  您瞧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.85,0:49:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多了这么多兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.39,0:49:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到与母亲见面
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.85,0:49:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.21,0:49:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.93,0:49:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都要垮掉了  还来
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.31,0:49:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.98,0:49:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.21,0:50:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.31,0:50:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.83,0:50:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想获得原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.25,0:50:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我想被原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.57,0:50:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.04,0:51:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然来了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.62,0:51:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来领孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.05,0:51:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼前这位
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.82,0:51:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.89,0:51:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.70,0:51:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾的是
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.28,0:51:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.75,0:51:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.70,0:53:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是救不了任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.47,0:53:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文森特  怎样一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.25,0:53:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我常来此地
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.63,0:54:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因而卡达裘们的一举一动我全看在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.85,0:54:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓星痕...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.83,0:54:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是排除体内异物的系统反应过剩所致
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.61,0:54:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体内也有类似LifeStraem的循环
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.57,0:54:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它与入侵的邪恶物质对峙
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.22,0:54:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪恶物质
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.65,0:54:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨菲罗斯因子  杰诺娃的遗传意念
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.95,0:54:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你怎么称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.43,0:54:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好详细
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.58,0:54:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾和伊利娜  
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.59,0:54:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奄奄一息着被搬到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.00,0:54:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必是被严加拷问的后果
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.48,0:54:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救倒是救了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.80,0:54:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生死难说
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.23,0:54:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拷问？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.17,0:54:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.66,0:54:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们入手了杰诺娃的头
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.75,0:54:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡达裘所找的母亲是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.89,0:55:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上天遣送的凶神恶煞——
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.19,0:55:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰诺娃
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.67,0:55:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用她造出第二个萨菲罗斯也不无可能
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.52,0:55:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡达裘...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.62,0:55:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.34,0:55:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想琢磨
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.90,0:55:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马琳
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.74,0:55:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.64,0:55:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹泽尔和蒂法她...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.48,0:55:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂法没有事
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.71,0:55:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟蒂法说话
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.19,0:55:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有手机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.18,0:55:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍天啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.95,0:55:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文森特  帮我把马琳送到店里
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.69,0:55:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去听听神罗有什么高见
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.73,0:55:51.86,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是上策
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.86,0:55:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.56,0:55:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了克劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.95,0:55:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么总是一意孤行
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.77,0:56:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马琳
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.45,0:56:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再忍耐一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.22,0:56:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗就要打响
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.47,0:56:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  光靠刀枪不能解决问题
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.85,0:56:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.82,0:56:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.18,0:56:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德  这关乎战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.53,0:56:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.93,0:56:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘却之都
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.69,0:56:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们老家
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.56,0:56:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.47,0:56:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去和路法斯谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.25,0:56:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.44,0:56:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.53,0:56:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了孩子们可能也无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.30,0:56:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次酿出无法挽回的事也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.89,0:56:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你害怕这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.29,0:56:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  请你面对复杂的现实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.12,0:56:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负担重？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.04,0:56:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重是应该的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.08,0:56:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学不会一个人生活就要学会忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.71,0:56:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明耐不住寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.27,0:56:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不接  手机却从不离身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.74,0:57:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们老家  你还不快去
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.89,0:57:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我们...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.91,0:57:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输给回忆不成
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.42,0:57:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我曾经见死不救啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.05,0:57:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拖拖拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.77,0:57:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快放过可怜的自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.23,0:57:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪能被原谅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.90,0:57:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曾尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.58,0:57:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝试？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.60,0:57:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.82,0:57:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马琳  我们回去
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.81,0:57:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来尝试一番
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.19,0:58:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果会联系给你
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.36,0:58:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是李富
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.04,0:58:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作顺畅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.32,0:58:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了下传单  好一个不赚钱的生意
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.72,0:58:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却也是克劳德先生的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.49,0:58:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很乐意尽一份绵薄之力  日后联系
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.06,0:58:36.98,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.35,0:58:38.68,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有工作委托你  好久不见  我是尤菲酱
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.91,0:58:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五台的孩子们失踪一事你清楚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.77,0:58:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我点消息哈  拜托咯
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.84,0:58:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级大  我有眉目了  过一段就去见马琳  帮我转达一下  挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.75,0:58:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己当心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.91,0:58:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来都没怨过你的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.25,0:58:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.04,0:58:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.74,0:59:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们聋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.32,0:59:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  装听不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.87,0:59:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做这种事要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.85,0:59:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对孩子做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.71,0:59:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有希
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.12,1:00:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹泽尔
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.59,1:00:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹泽尔
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.92,1:00:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹泽尔
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.94,1:01:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩什么呢
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.25,1:01:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈就在这儿吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.73,1:01:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说说思路
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.05,1:01:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个叫什么呢...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.77,1:01:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪念碑  是神罗造的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.41,1:01:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说藏在这里？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.63,1:01:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.09,1:01:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.33,1:01:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没被告诉
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.89,1:01:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧  果然是藏在某地
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.85,1:01:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁德  你来顶一句
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.67,1:02:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼吗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.78,1:02:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.21,1:02:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没有丹泽尔那么疼
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.20,1:02:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能治好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.17,1:02:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.01,1:02:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为了丹泽尔找遍了各种方法呢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.22,1:02:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.03,1:02:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你从来不收拾桌子
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.18,1:02:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.69,1:02:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德是因为丹泽尔的星痕治不好  所以离家出走的？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.90,1:02:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是因为自己也有了星痕
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.19,1:02:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.32,1:02:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己都照顾不过来
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.25,1:02:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一想就...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.66,1:03:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己都照顾不过来  还提什么保护家人！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.53,1:03:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老爹说的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.32,1:03:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德你别放弃
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.85,1:03:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马琳  丹泽尔  蒂法
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.25,1:03:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是在帮助我呢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.66,1:03:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是被人保护着
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.94,1:03:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回要轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.30,1:03:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.61,1:03:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  卡达裘
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.61,1:03:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你一件事
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.56,1:03:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此一件哦
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.33,1:03:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说过  要用杰诺娃细胞来复原
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.93,1:03:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该怎么理解？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.18,1:03:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他...会回来
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.87,1:04:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨菲罗斯  
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.07,1:04:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噩梦啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.48,1:04:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.88,1:04:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.13,1:04:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟萨菲罗斯没有瓜葛
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.56,1:04:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是对他有感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.07,1:04:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人心烦
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.86,1:04:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈青睐我和萨菲罗斯哪一个呢...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.81,1:04:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意念体真是可怜
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.25,1:04:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你们的下场只有一个
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.43,1:04:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈长途跋涉来到这个星球
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.47,1:04:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让愚蠢的家伙们灰飞烟灭
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.71,1:04:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.71,1:04:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里和妈妈来的时候相比丝毫没改善
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.27,1:04:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来博得母亲欢心
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.28,1:04:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对母亲...唯命是从
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.76,1:04:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  噩梦再临是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.96,1:05:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一日不消失  就会重蹈覆辙
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.42,1:05:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星球上循环往复的LifeStream
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.52,1:05:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在生死之间徘徊而无阻
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.53,1:05:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果生命的原貌就是这般周而复始
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.98,1:05:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那历史的重演也就是必然事件
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.41,1:05:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰诺娃也好萨菲罗斯也罢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.64,1:05:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管去惹是生非好了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.00,1:05:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会遵循生命的安排
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.18,1:05:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不厌其烦地挫败你们
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.09,1:05:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长  这是给抢走妈妈找托辞？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.92,1:05:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际却暗自后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.58,1:05:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后悔？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.71,1:05:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我乐此不疲
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.32,1:05:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再好不过
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.97,1:06:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  也该落幕了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.38,1:07:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹泽尔  我们得离开了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.73,1:07:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.76,1:07:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难度太大
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.49,1:08:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它来没？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.19,1:08:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没胆量看
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.96,1:09:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乐趣无穷啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.79,1:09:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊透顶啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.95,1:09:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有完没完
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.55,1:09:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实把母亲奉还就一了百了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.46,1:09:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们拿杰诺娃的头做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.36,1:09:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么再聚合  吃错药啦？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.31,1:10:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只想见见母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.47,1:10:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲会决定今后的所有事
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.94,1:10:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  母亲在哪
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.27,1:10:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲来母亲去的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.00,1:10:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是杰诺娃的项上人头么
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.88,1:10:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.70,1:10:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许这么称呼母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.06,1:10:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.26,1:10:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我错了  
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.58,1:10:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.52,1:10:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道什么鸟歉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.87,1:11:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂法？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.01,1:11:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王八蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.93,1:11:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这儿保护你妈
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.76,1:11:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴雷特
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.34,1:12:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马琳还好好的吧  啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.23,1:12:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不过啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.22,1:12:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我晕...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.58,1:12:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁动了我的磨石球
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.70,1:12:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用问  来者不善
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.51,1:12:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卧槽~
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.90,1:12:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.73,1:13:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型的  希艾拉号
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.56,1:13:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿让你们坐坐
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.08,1:13:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买电话怎么走
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.53,1:13:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.69,1:13:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是伙伴
