Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.74,1:13:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.38,1:13:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有完没完
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.13,1:13:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂法
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.35,1:14:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹泽尔
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.91,1:14:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
