Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.28,1:14:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.06,1:14:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻松了不少
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.77,1:15:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总拖来拖去  拖轻了包袱
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.09,1:15:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人回店里吧  
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.85,1:15:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟马琳等你们
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.23,1:15:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德也会回家吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.78,1:15:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.86,1:16:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会输给你啊
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.78,1:18:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点登场啊
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.26,1:19:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有意思啊  社长
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.44,1:19:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来召唤什么好
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.96,1:19:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.81,1:19:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都没发现  不孝顺
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.53,1:19:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宰了它  克劳德
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.80,1:19:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
