Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.86,1:28:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.31,1:28:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很强大吗
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.83,1:28:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凝聚了神罗的科技与汗水
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.41,1:28:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你研发的么
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.02,1:28:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威力姑且不说  华丽得很
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.94,1:28:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.10,1:28:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吧  搭档
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.21,1:28:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可以告别加班咯
