Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.34,1:33:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无二致
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.40,1:33:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德  磨石球在此
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.10,1:33:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别摇晃啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.65,1:33:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希德  快降落
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.33,1:33:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  自己不会跳啊  跳
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.23,1:33:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别插手
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.04,1:33:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.54,1:33:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是萨菲罗斯的意念体
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.64,1:33:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好比是幼虫
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.85,1:33:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼虫
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.86,1:33:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫子  他是虫子啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.28,1:33:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘  安静点
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.71,1:33:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚变身成萨菲罗斯么
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.45,1:34:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说  克劳德知道这事吗
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.53,1:34:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕知情
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.21,1:34:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.88,1:34:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我们不插手
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.58,1:34:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理解不能  快说明下
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.56,1:34:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人的话题
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.93,1:34:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性别歧视  大男子主义
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.92,1:34:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘  闭上嘴
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.95,1:34:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷们儿也蒙在鼓里
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.08,1:34:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2年前
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.87,1:34:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终决战的时候明明有过的斗志
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.31,1:34:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却被短短的两年时间冲淡了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.61,1:34:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想克劳德又点燃了斗志
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.86,1:34:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  我忍他10分钟
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.47,1:34:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德事儿真多
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.89,1:34:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这叫坦率
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.22,1:36:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的再结合
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.45,1:36:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你见识一番
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.34,1:36:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久违了啊  克劳德
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.65,1:36:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消了星痕啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.70,1:36:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不胜惋惜
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.43,1:36:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的何在
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.40,1:36:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死在星痕之下的亡魂
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.05,1:36:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴着LifeStream巡行在这个星球
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.99,1:37:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚侵蚀星球
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.46,1:37:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德  我的愿望是
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.91,1:37:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以星球作舟  向宇宙的黑暗启航
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.51,1:37:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如当年的母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.57,1:37:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们早晚会物色好另一颗星球
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.05,1:37:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里创造繁花似锦的未来
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.42,1:37:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的星球会怎样
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.37,1:37:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道  看你本事了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.77,1:37:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.57,1:38:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？  什么使你变强了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.18,1:38:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懒得和你说
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.20,1:39:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在物色送你的见面礼
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.84,1:39:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送你「绝望」如何？
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.15,1:39:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跪地求饶给我看
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.28,1:41:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当年的疼痛你可曾记得  克劳德
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.67,1:41:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻再次  赐予你刻骨铭心的痛
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.15,1:42:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你而言什么最重要？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.44,1:42:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我夺来快乐一下如何
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.17,1:42:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换做是我  绝对不放弃
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.57,1:42:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便情形很绝望
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.67,1:42:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握紧你的梦想
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.59,1:42:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时刻与战士的荣耀同在
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.44,1:42:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  虽没成为战士  也不妨抱着那颗心
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.47,1:42:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎克斯
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.46,1:42:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我帮你一把？
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.24,1:43:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手下败将而已  轻松搞定他
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.88,1:43:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:43:14.54,1:43:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再忘了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.63,1:43:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你生命的见证
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.94,1:43:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲啊  你一无所知
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.31,1:43:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都很珍贵
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.96,1:44:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在回忆中安息吧
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.70,1:44:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.11,1:44:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会成为回忆
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.14,1:45:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.90,1:45:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡达裘
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.46,1:45:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.82,1:45:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也该放弃努力了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.37,1:45:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妈妈...吗
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.34,1:45:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回大家身边吧
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.51,1:45:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.51,1:47:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  知道厉害了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.81,1:47:03.87,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的没错吧
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.02,1:47:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯爷们儿~  克劳德是纯爷们儿~
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.46,1:47:08.04,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德想做就能成功
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.76,1:47:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个抓稳了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.93,1:47:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都守候在我们身边吧
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.63,1:47:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.81,1:47:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.65,1:48:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.79,1:48:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起玩
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.78,1:48:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.08,1:48:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳德也会回家吧
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.26,1:49:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.25,1:49:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.22,1:50:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.10,1:50:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还这么叫
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.47,1:50:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三番五次叫我妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.09,1:50:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不好  多亲切
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.74,1:50:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大的孩子要不起
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.89,1:51:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾  你不属于这儿
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.52,1:52:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐说克劳德会来这里
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.76,1:52:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.89,1:52:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:26.77,1:52:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些孩子还留有星痕
Dialogue: 0,1:52:30.31,1:52:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.49,1:52:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  让他帮你治好
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.44,1:52:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以放心了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.94,1:52:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.71,1:53:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.01,1:53:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都给我跳进去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.22,1:53:45.61,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治好了治好了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:33.49,1:54:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后  没问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.41,1:54:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.52,1:55:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.85,1:55:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,2000)}并不孤单
